window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Listen to Buryoku book 7-9 now in one convenient Box Set!</p> <p>The competition between the Scions of Safaia and the Ancient Cavern Beast Furea is about to begin.</p> <p>Thrown into the tournament, Roy finds that there are more than a few challengers who outclass him. The secret to victory lies between the pages of an ancient book and newly-awakened senses he does not fully understand.</p> <p>All the while, a sinister voice not belonging to Geon whispers in his mind.</p> <p>The tournament will test Roy and his allies as never before and with the fate of the continent on the line, they will need to advance, or be washed away in the tide of carnage that will follow.</p>"; 
